{"tid":2025712,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[鍾培生香港電競] 希望下次創科局開會叫埋我","createTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:57:02.000Z","uid":74218,"like":151,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"4b784572817a69b47d2b25c17b0d46fd4ab521e1","tid":2025712,"uid":74218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"回應一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/500787548/posts/10157475820502549/?d=w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F500787548%2Fposts%2F10157475820502549%2F%3Fd%3Dw&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9d58eba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/500787548/posts/10157475820502549/?d=w</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsxPCma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsxPCma.jpg&h=a7d49215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AKa6ew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AKa6ew.jpg&h=fe99e699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創科局FB<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ITBHK/posts/2563544973895984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FITBHK%2Fposts%2F2563544973895984&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=4874e59d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ITBHK/posts/2563544973895984</a><br />\n<br />\n淺談電競<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j68EWmaspWY&amp;t=27s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj68EWmaspWY%26t%3D27s&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=c4365ab5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j68EWmaspWY&amp;t=27s</a><br />\n<br />\n之前Youtube 拍淺談電競, 當中都有提到香港政府推動電競, 有心了解行業嘅朋友不妨可以參考下Subcribe 我Channel<br />\n<br />\n創科局個post 話開會傾點推電競, 本人想跟返個post問下相入面嘅人幾條問題?<br />\n<br />\n如何加強電競人才培育?<br />\n<br />\n請問邊個帶領過香港選手進LOL世界賽?<br />\n請問邊個培育過職業傳說對決選手?<br />\n請問邊個培育過職業皇室戰爭選手?<br />\n請問邊個培育過職業OW 選手?<br />\n請問邊個培育過職業CS選手?<br />\n請問邊個培育過職業爐石戰記選手?<br />\n<br />\n請問依家各遊戲職業聯賽中幾多人HKA出黎?<br />\n請問依家電競行業中幾多人HKEsports出黎?<br />\n<br />\n如何發展電競周邊產業鏈嘅商機?<br />\n<br />\n請問邊個有跨國電競媒體?<br />\n請問邊個投資過國際嘅電競公司?<br />\n請問邊個開發過電競Apps?<br />\n請問邊個以香港電競命名亞洲首橦電競大樓?<br />\n<br />\n如何吸引更多國際賽事來港?<br />\n請問邊個搞過國際性賽事?<br />\n請問邊個將最高認受性嘅LMS帶黎香港?<br />\n<br />\n請問圖中嘅人同電競產業有咩關係?<br />\n<br />\n創科局話拎一億推動電競, 當中用左5千萬裝修數碼港嘅電競場地<br />\n除此之外啲錢仲點樣培育人才, 點樣發展商機同點樣提高國際地位?<br />\n請問成功搞過啲咩出黎?<br />\n請問除左裝修, 呢一億洗左去邊度?<br />\n請問以咩準則去衡量由邊個拎錢?<br />\n請問咩項目拎左錢?<br />\n請問邊個拎過啲錢?<br />\n<br />\n我2013年2月成立HKEsports, 出左唔止一億推動香港電競, 無拎過政府一分一毫, 但以上我通通都做到<br />\n<br />\n下次開會記得叫埋我<br />\n<br />\n支持業界喺疫情穩住發展，我哋期望同業界一齊努力😉💪🏼"},{"pid":"4b56147a10670e0664165ea399c7fdf4a9cc0bda","tid":2025712,"uid":60133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"遊戲設計好有條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8efafbe38993309ee09b43e17319d1166f69d6","tid":2025712,"uid":276179,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"鍾生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dac750079e13fa5780b6da16496acea136ba9c","tid":2025712,"uid":72000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"又live左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 不如鐘生開下youtube live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d34b308a341f63a393fb5ce24f37541d38b892","tid":2025712,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"鍾生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e2d37f85236d45ba674a32d7e380daf67347bf","tid":2025712,"uid":253135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:38:01.000Z",